WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Dodecagon' is a Workbench game where the goal is to link all
12 tiles with each other of a dodecagon shaped board, making a
total of 66 links. The least amount of moves it takes to complete
the game, the better it is... but there are no restrictions, so
you can move on already linked tiles or links anytime you like...

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Various size and shapes of game boards.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it doesn't take ages to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

